#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:1
msgid "Panoramica"
msgstr "Overview"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:3
msgid "Scopo"
msgstr "Purpose"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:5
msgid "Calcolare la media aritmetica di `x` oppure, se `w` e presente, la media pesata."
msgstr "Compute the arithmetic mean of `x` or, if `w` is provided, the weighted mean."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:7
msgid "Parametri"
msgstr "Parameters"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:9
msgid "`x`: dati numerici."
msgstr "`x`: numeric data."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:10
msgid "`w`: pesi opzionali. Devono avere la stessa forma di `x` ed essere strettamente positivi."
msgstr "`w`: optional weights. They must have the same shape as `x` and be strictly positive."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:12
msgid "Restituisce"
msgstr "Returns"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:14
msgid "Un `float` con la media semplice o pesata."
msgstr "A `float` with the simple or weighted mean."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:16
msgid "Errori ed eccezioni"
msgstr "Errors and exceptions"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:18
msgid "`ValueError` se `x` e vuoto o non finito."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `x` is empty or not finite."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:19
msgid "`ValueError` se `w` ha forma incompatibile."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `w` has an incompatible shape."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:20
msgid "`ValueError` se `w` contiene valori non positivi o ha somma non positiva."
msgstr "`ValueError` if `w` contains non-positive values or has a non-positive sum."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:22
msgid "Esempio"
msgstr "Example"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:34
msgid "Note"
msgstr "Notes"

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:36
msgid "Se `w is None`, la funzione usa `numpy.mean`."
msgstr "If `w is None`, the function uses `numpy.mean`."

#: ../../source/moduli/stats_utils/weighted-mean/panoramica.md:37
msgid ""
"La validazione dei pesi passa per [`_validate_weights`](../../../checks/stats_utils/validate-"
"weights.md)."
msgstr ""
"Weight validation goes through [`_validate_weights`](../../../checks/stats_utils/validate-"
"weights.md)."

